==English==

===Etymology===
[[account]] + [[-ancy]]

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun|accountancies|-}}

# {{uncountable}} {{British}} The function of compiling and providing financial information primarily by reports referred to as financial statements. Accounting includes bookkeeping, systems design, analysis and interpretation of accounting information.
# {{countable}} A company or organisation that performs such a function.

